OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms' energy bills to be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcut by half this winter    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy bills for UK businesses will be 
OL,6, cut by around half their expected level
OL,7, this winter under a huge government    
OL,8, support package.                       
OL,10,FThe scheme will fix wholesale gas and  
OL,11,Felectricity prices for firms for six   
OL,12,Fmonths from 1 October, shielding       
OL,13,Fbusinesses from crippling costs.       
OL,15,FHospitals, schools and charities will  
OL,16,Falso get help, the government said.    
OL,18,FIt comes after ministers announced a   
OL,19,F#150bn plan to help households with    
OL,20,Ftheir soaring bills for two years.     
